              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Let's solve the equation:\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nThis is a transcendental equation (involving both a trigonometric and polynomial term), so it is best solved numerically.\n\nLet's find the real solutions for \\( x \\).",
